INTRODUCTION
============

This plugin can validate more deeper. You can set your own regular expression
for attributes. For example, you want limit users to post Flash videos only
from YouTube or Google, then you can restrain the src attribute.

DOCUMENTATION
=============

Please visit
  http://code.google.com/p/llbbsc/wiki/HTMLTagAttributesValidatorPlugin

